|               |             AggregateExec: mode=Partial, gby=[WatchID@0 as WatchID, ClientIP@1 as ClientIP], aggr=[count(Int64(1)), sum(hits.IsRefresh), avg(hits.ResolutionWidth)]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
